In the src directory with a linux operating system type make clean

To start the game type the below with 4100 being whatever you set the port too.

nohup ./startup 6dragons 4100 &

I added a Admin player with password 12345

just change password, and pcrename command for your name or adjust name in 6dragons/players/a/Admin file.

 
